{
  "text": "\u22121 ds. Let N = e m be the inward pointing unit normal vector on \u2202M and e i , 1 \u2264 i \u2264 m \u2212 1 be the orthonormal frame on T (\u2202M ). Let L ab = (\u2207 ea e b , N ) be the second fundamental form and indices {a, b, \u00b7 \u00b7 \u00b7} range from 1 through m \u2212 1. We use [CITATION_1] Thm 1.1 ] to obtain the first five coefficients of the heat trace asymptotics: ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "5196312"
  },
  "bib_entries": {
    "5196312": {
      "title": "The asymptotics of the Laplacian on a manifold with boundary",
      "abstract": "We study the fifth term in the asymptotic expansion of the heat operator trace for a partial differential operator of Laplace type on a compact Riemannian manifold with Dirichlet or Neumann boundary conditions."
    }
  }
}